libdrm installing 
from archive 
1. cd /tmp && wget http://dri.freedesktop.org/libdrm/libdrm-[verison].tar.bz2
3. tar -xvjf libdrm-[verison].tar.bz2
2. cd libdrm-[version] &&  sed -e "/pthread-stubs/d" -i configure.ac && autoreconf -fiv && ./configure --prefix=/usr --enable-udev && make
3. make install (as root)

include directories :
/usr/include/libkms  and /usr/include/libdrm